_min=10^9 M_sun in ionized regions and\nM_min=10^8 M_sun in neutral regions) than the case in which these small halos\nwere unsuppressed. In all cases, we do not see a turn-over toward high l in the\nshape of l^2 C_l.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Dec 2011 10:29:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Apr 2012 12:27:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-04-18"}
