ms of non-linear partial difference equations. We make use of a test set\nbased on the discretization of concrete systems of non-linear partial\ndifferential equations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Dec 2011 10:31:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Nov 2012 12:50:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 30 May 2013 17:22:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2013 14:59:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-24"}
